cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "UPV-EARTH: Mapping University Research onto the Planetary Boundaries"
message: "If you use this work, please cite it as below."
type: software
abstract: >-
  An institutional-intelligence pipeline that classifies the scientific
  production of the Universitat Politecnica de Valencia against the nine
  Planetary Boundaries. It combines corpus construction and cleaning, an
  operational PB ontology with activation and exclusion rules, lexical and
  scientific-embedding baselines, local LLM classification under an
  operational-object criterion with abstention, an auditable agent cascade,
  a web platform for review, and an economic feasibility analysis.
